title: Entangling
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

When a model is engaged in close combat against a model with or wielding a weapon with this special rule, its Attacks characteristic is reduced by one, to a minimum of 1. This effect does not stack with itself, but it may stack with other effects that lower Attacks.